sentences:
Algester is an outer suburb of City of Brisbane , Queensland , Australia .
It is south - west of the central business district .
The suburb 's population was 8,433 at the 2016 census .
The suburbs of Algester , Calamvale and now Parkinson , sit on the southern border or boundary of the City of Brisbane local government area with suburbs of Logan City such as Browns Plains and Regents Park .
The suburb 's name is a corruption of the name of the English town of " Alcester " .
Briefly in the mid - to - late-1970s the suburb was colloquially named Ridgewood Heights after the Ridgewood Heights property development that then made up most of its land area , but had officially been known as Algester from 1972 .
